The paper discusses the application of DSP to signals on graphs, which falls under the category of signal processing. Therefore, cs.SI (Signal Processing) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with data analysis and prediction, which could fall under cs.SD (Data Analysis, Statistics and Probability) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The use of graphs and networks suggests that the paper could also be classified under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
